snippet.title: Starcremental - Video
snippet.description:
Starcremental is an idle incremental game. Take Actions to complete Missions until your Morale falls so low that you experience a Mutiny. Re-spec and restart using the bonuses to Action Speed and Morale you have gained.

Available on Steam!
